Date: Fri, 11 Oct 2024 14:48:08 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] ESQL: Push down filters even in case of renames in Evals
 (#114411)

Optimize queries like
... | EVAL b = a, c = b | WHERE c > 2
to
... | WHERE a > 2 | EVAL b = a, c = b
